{"tid":2430253,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–雙面人抗體","createTime":"2021-03-02T21:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T06:12:28.000Z","uid":38861,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bbf00cb410d6296b0efb1adea7b0aa7ce532b989","tid":2430253,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T21:45:49.000Z","msg":"其中一道腫瘤形成的理論，就是經過無數基因異變的洗滌下，有助癌細胞生長的基因(Oncogene)不斷產生出來對它們有利的蛋白質，而負責抑制癌細胞生長的基因(Tumor Suppressor)則失去功用，沒能產生出制衝它們的蛋白質。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0UTTKaS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0UTTKaS.jpg&h=eb3c264e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在製藥角度來看，對付Oncogene常理上較為合理，畢竟抑制事物比起激發事物會來得更為容易。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）P53蛋白質是其中一隻Tumor Suppressor，它最常見的變異版本就R175H，意思是它的第175個氨基酸發生了異變。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d6TXrpf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6TXrpf.jpg&h=8ec8e446&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nP53蛋白質延伸閱讀:<br />\n分半鐘科學&ndash;缺氧對癌細胞的好處<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2420256\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2420256</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然P53蛋白質主要是位於細胞內部，但當中會有一小節的蛋白質會表達在細胞表面上，名為新生抗原(Neoantigen)，數量極為稀少，可以少至1顆細胞只有10塊表達在其表面上。<br />\n<br />\n現時有科學家開始從針對Tumor Suppressor入手，製作出「雙面人」抗體(Bispecific antibodies)，一面辨認癌細胞的新生抗原，另一面則會辨認免疫細胞T cell，目的就是希望透過雙面人抗體拉近免疫細胞與癌細胞的距離，促使免疫細胞更有效率地對癌細胞進行皇天擊殺。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）對老鼠注射平均表面每顆平均只有2塊變種版本新生抗原的癌細胞，七日後可從螢光技術見得到腫瘤有著增大的趨勢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6HLOx4m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6HLOx4m.png&h=31cd0782&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而注射能辨認P53蛋白質R175H變種的雙面人抗體後，腫瘤體積顯著有所減少。<br />\n<br />\n這技術的好處是能夠針對殺滅擁有特定變異基因的癌細胞，但基於每顆癌細胞的變異位置及程度均有所不同，要活用這技術的話便必須要獲取該病人的癌細胞基因變異狀況。<br />\n<br />\n螢光技術延伸閱讀:<br />\n三十秒科學&ndash;透視癌細胞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2408323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2408323</a><br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiutqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=a9bf5b87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiutqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=edbb1afe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://science.sciencemag.org/content/early/2021/02/26/science.abc8697\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscience.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2Fearly%2F2021%2F02%2F26%2Fscience.abc8697&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiutqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=ed8a9716\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://science.sciencemag.org/content/early/2021/02/26/science.abc8697</a>"},{"pid":"3bb256aa6cf362ed480e055b10696e10f6da34a8","tid":2430253,"uid":199689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T21:48:13.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44d9a42b71f060ba0f1078d5565b4c416f30c68","tid":2430253,"uid":302951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T21:54:34.0